    To use proxy65, several items must be set as part of proxy65_flags
    in rc.conf.

    The available flags are:
	--jid=	    [Jabber ID of the service, def "proxy65"]
	--secret=   [shared secret with the S2S]
	--rhost=    [Host of the Jabber service router, default "localhost"]
	--rport=    [port of the Jabber service router, default 5347]
	--proxyips= [proxy address:ports to be advertised/used]

    --secret and --proxyips options are required.

    ex:
	proxy6_flags="--jid=proxy.jabber.example.org \
			--secret=JabberSecret \
			--rhost=jabber.example.org \
			--rport=5347 \
			--proxyips=172.17.233.23:8010"

===========================================================================
